  <brief_title>Non--operative Treatment of the Medial Malleolus in bi- and Trimalleolar Ankle Fractures</brief_title>
  <official_title>Non--operative Treatment of the Medial Malleolus in bi- and Trimalleolar Ankle Fractures. A Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
