  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study was to determine if internal fixation of the medial malleolus is
      necessary following open reduction and internal fixation of the lateral and, if required, the
      posterior malleolus treating displaced bi-or trimalleolar ankle fractures.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
